    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite six credibility factors remaining unassessed and all seven assessed factors falling below required levels, the assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile on the basis that the model is used only for exploratory clinical research ranking of pump geometries, not for direct regulatory submission. The team noted that the absence of a structured ContextOfUse record limits traceability of this decision to any specific intended-use scope; the use context is described only in the package narrative.",
